      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level of 2 for MRL 3.",
      "rationale": "Validation experiments conducted on the same FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under clinically representative CPB flow and speed ranges. Fluid analogue (porcine blood at physiological hematocrit) closely replicates COU conditions."
