      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level of 2 for MRL 3.",
      "rationale": "Three independent experimental replicates performed at each of the 5 operating points. Inter-replicate variability in RH index reported and shown to be within ±8%. Sample preparation protocol documented with hematocrit and osmolality verification."
