      "rationale": "Assessment of use error was considered beyond the scope of the current submission. The team noted that a structured analyst error analysis (e.g., review of simulation setup checklists against a formal use-error taxonomy) had not been conducted within the project timeline. This factor is deferred to a subsequent credibility assessment cycle. No concrete mitigation or bounding argument is provided."
    },
    {
