      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not established for this submission cycle; factor carried as not-assessed.",
      "rationale": "Formal model form uncertainty analysis (e.g., comparison of power-law hemolysis model against alternative strain-based or energy-dissipation models) was identified as beyond scope for the current assessment. The selection of the Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law constants was not subjected to sensitivity analysis. This factor is deferred pending availability of multi-model comparison data."
