    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-cardiovascular-simulation-group-lead",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team determined that the 10 assessed factors collectively demonstrate sufficient evidence to support the intended use of the CFD model for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions at MRL 3. Three factors (Use error, Model form, Equivalency of input parameters) remain not-assessed; the team noted these were beyond the scope of the current submission cycle but did not provide concrete justification for why their absence does not materially affect credibility at the elevated Model Risk Level 3. The decision to accept was made on the basis of the assessed factors meeting or exceeding required levels.",
